# HRV Agentic Intelligence System — Build Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A production-grade multi-agent AI system for clinical HRV-based sepsis risk detection, targeting the WHOOP AI Engineer portfolio. Built at `/Users/yashnayi/Desktop/HRV/hrv-agent/`.

